des:
With the LEDVANCE SMART+ Skill you can control the SMART+ WiFi products with Alexa app or voice. 

After connecting Alexa to your LEDVANCE SMART+ WiFi products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our ""LEDVANCE SMART+"" app in Android or iOS app market;
(2) Register one account in our ""LEDVANCE SMART+"" app;
(3) You need to have some devices in hand;
(4) Configure these devices in our ""LEDVANCE SMART+"" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in ""LEDVANCE SMART+"" skills;
(5) Download Amazon ""Alexa"" app from Android, iOS or Amazon app market;
(6) Configure Echo with ""Alexa"" app;
(7) Search ""LEDVANCE SMART+"" skill from the ""Alexa"" app skills category;
(8) Click Enable skill of ""LEDVANCE SMART+"", and you'll be navigated to our login page;
(9) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking；
(10) Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
